com.here.android.mpa.venues3d

Class VenueRouteStyleOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.venues3d.VenueRouteStyleOptions

  • public class VenueRouteStyleOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines style options for the key points of the CombinedRoute. Defines the pack of MapObject prototypes that are used for customizing the map objects, which are displayed on the key points of the CombinedRoute. By default all the prototypes are null, which means that default MapMarker objects will be used for those prototypes. The term "prototype" means that the provided MapObject will not be used directly on the map, but instead each time when this instance of VenueRouteStyleOptions is passed to RoutingController.showRoute(CombinedRoute, VenueRouteStyleOptions), the copy of this prototype will be created and this copy will be displayed on the specific point along the route.
    Note:
    All the MapObject prototypes accept only objects, which are inherited from MapMarker or MapLocalModel.
